    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自从三十年前飞艇发明以来，世界发生了变化。蒸汽动力飞艇现在遍布天空。曾经只是天空中一个斑点的漂浮岛屿现在触手可及。从不可预测的云海和其中蕴含的危险中找到回家的路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主要特性:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·         包含任务、制作和谜题的独立 ARPG</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·         乘坐原始蒸汽朋克飞艇和步行探索开放世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·         贸易和收集资源</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·         管理飞艇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·         参加飞艇对飞艇战斗以及近战和远程战斗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·         单人游玩或分屏合作<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893390/extras/bd58ebfd3bc5c99ffa58bb980468b361.avif?t=1770971877\" width=600 height=125 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893390/extras/7179b7c30d6e3c16c63e7e9f4beb0363.poster.avif?t=1770971877\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893390/extras/7179b7c30d6e3c16c63e7e9f4beb0363.webm?t=1770971877\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893390/extras/7179b7c30d6e3c16c63e7e9f4beb0363.mp4?t=1770971877\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893390/extras/3235caeaf52194a1f0bf00826f8894e8.avif?t=1770971877\" width=600 height=125 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893390/extras/68126f7c45d284548970cc655657cb1a.poster.avif?t=1770971877\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/stea